timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 22' Plenty of possession for Houston, but nothing doing so far. Laredo looking useful on the break. 0-0 #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 23' - Bruin lays a ball off to Barnes in the box, who puts a first time shot just wide. Giles has stayed down. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 25' Barnes back up on his feet after some attention from the trainer. Walks off to the touchline. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 26' Thankfully, it looks like Giles is going to come back on. 0-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 28' Driver gets into the box, cuts the ball back, but nobody is there for Houston. 0-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 32' Yellow card for Braem after a rash challenge on Barnes. Nothing comes of the resulting free kick. 0-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 35' More set pieces for Houston. Another corner, followed by another free kick coming up. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 36' Nothing comes of yet another corner. Laredo defending well. Houston being patient in possession. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 37' Alex Lopez scores a delightful chip after a lay off by Omar Cummings. His first ever Dynamo goal. 1-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Two places to watch tonight's match: http://t.co/3SUy8RGFDI | http://t.co/FMW32AHkQ5 #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 40' RED CARD for Laredo. Matthiew Braem has been booked for his second bookable offense. 1-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Tonight's @DiscountTire Halftime Score: Houston Dynamo 1-0 Laredo Heat. Alex Lopez, y'all. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.comment: First Half ends, Houston Dynamo 1, Laredo Heat 0.

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: That chip. Watch it: http://t.co/ugKWLxOdyE #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 45' We're back underway for the second half. Watch it live: http://t.co/R5qJC3aai3 #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Second Half begins Houston Dynamo 1, Laredo Heat 0.

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 6' Another Dynamo corner coming. Bright start for the men in orange. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 52' Red card to Tyler Deric. He handled outside of the box after giving the ball away. Tally Hall about to come on. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 53' SUB: Tally Hall comes on for Omar Cummings after the red card to Tyler Deric. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Back to happy stuff. Alex celebrates his goal. (via @DomsDisciples) #ForeverOrange #USOC2014 http://t.co/cQNyt8CfYV

timelineItems.text: Back to happy stuff. Alex celebrates his goal. (via @DomsDisciples) #ForeverOrange #USOC2014 http://t.co/cQNyt8CfYV

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: From @houstondash to Dynamo. #ForeverOrange #DashOn https://t.co/PudEXn8fKJ

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 63' Not a lot happening. Couple set pieces here and there. Still 1-0 Dynamo. 10 v 10. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Double the fun. About to get #USOC2014 started. #ForeverOrange http://t.co/bjWU1ZBEXH

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Double the fun. About to get #USOC2014 started. #ForeverOrange http://t.co/bjWU1ZBEXH

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 64' SUB: Brian Ownby coming on for Alex Lopez. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Teams are coming out soon. We'll be live shortly at http://t.co/mQC9pwxScG! #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 1' We're underway at BBVA Compass Stadium. Driver with a chance immediately in the first minute. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 68' Ownby makes a patented move down the right flank, takes a cross-shot that ends up going out for a goal kick. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 71' Confusion at the front post for Laredo. Nothing doing, but Warren almost sneaks in to create a real chance. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 75' Double chance for Driver! A good save from the Laredo keeper, followed by a volley going JUST wide. 1-0. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 75' SUB: Jason Johnson comes on for Giles Barnes. 1-0. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 9' Nervy moment in the back for Houston. Kofi eventually knocks it behind for a Laredo corner. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 81' Close call. Bruin takes a half volley from just inside the box. It whistles just wide of the far post. 1-0. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Lineups are announced and players are warming up.

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 5 minutes of normal time to go. Still 1-0 Dynamo. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: 9' Villavicencio gets his head on the corner, but it goes over Deric's crossbar. 0-0. #USOC2014 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: FULL TIME! Houston Dynamo 1-0 Laredo Heat. We move on to host FC Dallas or San Antonio on June 24 or 25. #ForeverOrange #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Houston Dynamo 1, Laredo Heat 0.
